data.description: ***VA ASSUMABLE LOAN AVAILABLE TO VA BUYERS*** NO FLOOD ZONE SO NO FLOOD INSURANCE NEEDED HERE! TRIPLE LOT!! This lot is roughly 120 ft wide so you have plenty of space for dockage and/or larger vessels than the standard lot does! Sitting high and dry in the highly desired Cornwallis area offering *DIRECT GULF ACCESS* Which is the only type of access you want!!! Never worry about getting stuck on the way home because you can’t clear bridges at high tide! This renovated 4 bedroom 3 bath home has it all! Inside you’ll find two master bedrooms. Two laundry rooms, one in garage and one inside. Timeless renovations that include wood look tile floors, shiplap on the ceiling inside and out, beautiful oak colored cabinets, granite countertops, plantation shutters, and the list goes on, Outside you’ll find that the Tiki hut is new with electrical wired with a projector and screen built into the hut. A pavered pool deck, the pool has a swim spa, with a new motor just installed. Additional parking. 30amp RV hookup on the side of the house. Captains walk dock with additional cantilever dock. Roof was last done in 2018, hurricane shutters, Roof 2018, AC 2021, and many more upgrades!
